rows.label: tev040701_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Galba about the Ganglion.

rows.label: tev040701_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Galba about the Cavern Clan.

rows.label: tev040701_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Galba about recent developments.

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0001
rows.name:
Cavern Clan destroyed our home.
Ganglion sent forces to help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0002
rows.name:
Ganglion's leader was female named Goetia.
She reminded me of ogpodus.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0003
rows.name:
...Hmm? You have never heard of ogpodus?
It is beast from our homeworld.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0004
rows.name:
Ogpodus has 16 tentacles that crush life from you.
Nasty creature.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0005
rows.name:
Goetia was ogpodus in every way. She attacked us
without mercy. Women. Children. None were spared.
She laughed as she killed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0009
rows.name:
My wife was enslaved by Cavern Clan.
Made to work on fortress day and night without sleep.
When she died, she had no strength left.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0010
rows.name: Nemard and Duna also lost parents during battle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0011
rows.name: And my father. Auld Belgazus, was near death.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0012
rows.name: But I must stay strong. Show way for young Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0017
rows.name: Earth alien! You slew Goetia and her Skell![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0018
rows.name:
You took vengeance on Ganglion demon who stole
our home![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0019
rows.name:
I do not know how you did this with bodies so small.
But I thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0020
rows.name: Now souls of butchered kin can rest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0025
rows.name: Strongest Cavern Clan warrior is Dadaan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0026
rows.name:
His name is legend on homeworld of Tormein.
Only spoken in whisper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0027
rows.name:
He was mighty sight in battle. Laid waste to Tree Clan.
Killed men. Stole women for his own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0028
rows.name:
Ganglion captured Dadaan. But he escaped.
Now he roams free in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG0029
rows.name:
I will not let Dadaan harm Duna or Liana.
I will die to save them![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG1001
rows.name: Nemard came to me. Asked for combat lessons.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG1002
rows.name: Now I train him like newly tamed beast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG1003
rows.name: Heh. He gave up sloth quickly for sake of female.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG1004
rows.name:
But I humor Nemard. Teach him all I know.
Soon he will be powerful warrior like you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG2001
rows.name:
My father, Auld Belgazus, was good leader.
Proud warrior.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG2002
rows.name:
He raced across wastelands. Ran through forests.
Beheaded Cavern Clan everywhere.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG2003
rows.name:
Now he is one with jacul. New beasts will serve him!
He will tear across skies of Oblivia! Bwa ha ha![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040701_MSG2004
rows.name:
Thank you, Earth alien. You did well.
You returned his flesh to strong beast indeed![ST:wait ]
